Data Automation

Python automation project for retrieving and downloading court-related documents from the Mahkamah Agung (Supreme Court of Indonesia) website.

Key Features

- Automated website navigation
- Automated document retrieval
- Automated file downloading
- Organized storage of downloaded files

Tech Stack
- Python
- Playwright
- SeleniumBase

Project Structure

text
Data_Automation
├── ma_scraper.py
├── sb_Mahkamah_Agung.py
├── downloads/
└── downloaded_files/

Getting Started

bash
git clone https://github.com/Franlyjoshua/Data_Automation.git
cd Data_Automation

python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate

pip install -r requirements.txt


Run the automation:

bash
python ma_scraper.py

